      <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 16px;">
        Legal translation plays a pivotal role in the UAE's legal framework due to the nation's diverse cultural landscape and the coexistence of both Arabic and English as official languages. The primary purpose of legal translation services in the UAE is to bridge linguistic gaps and facilitate seamless communication across language barriers within the legal domain.
      </p>
      <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">
        Index Office Service specializes in legal translations, boasting a team of experienced translators well-versed in legal terminology and nuances — ensuring accurate, contextually sound, and culturally sensitive translations for individuals and businesses alike.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="position:relative;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <img src="/images/img-55.webp" alt="Legal Translation UAE" style="width:100%;height:400px;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
      <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent 40%,rgba(26,32,44,0.75) 100%);"></div>
      <div style="position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:20px;right:20px;">
        <p style="color:#fff;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 4px;">Professional Legal Translation Assistance</p>
        <p style="color:#B2F5EA;font-size:0.75rem;margin:0;">Arabic · English · Courts · Ministries · Immigration</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ PURPOSE & BENEFITS ════ -->
<section style="background:#fff;padding:76px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,transparent,transparent 48px,rgba(56,178,172,0.04) 48px,rgba(56,178,172,0.04) 49px);pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
