      <div style="position:absolute;top:50%;left:40px;transform:translateY(-50%);">
        <p style="color:#38B2AC;font-weight:700;font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 6px;">Purpose &amp; Significance</p>
        <h2 style="color:#fff;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2rem);font-weight:900;margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.25;">WHY LEGAL TRANSLATION MATTERS IN THE UAE</h2>
